<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann Adolf von Nassau, Propst von SS. Peter und Paul in Jechaburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Wilhelm II. Rummel und Hans Prünster, Bürger zu Nürnberg, alle Forderungen erfüllt haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_528" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Johan Adolff von Naſſawe Sıgeler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l2">cʒu Hoeſte vnd Probiſt cʒu Jecheburgk </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l3">Erſamer vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr </del> wir euch vormals <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l4"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von wilhelm Rumels des <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd Hanſen Prünſters </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> wegen / Darauff Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> y </del> vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> wider <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l6">habt / ob <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe cʒetele </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l10">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>auſʒweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l9">ynnehellet </ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">der </del> / die Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l8">vnd wir haben </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vns vormals geſant habt / heten </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l7">oder ob </ab></add> ſie 
<del rend="strikethrough">aber </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l12">des noch niht getan 
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1576347448516_3167"><expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> daʒ ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das noch 
<del rend="strikethrough"> teten </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l11">tun </ab></add> / ſo vvolt Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l13">ein genüg daran <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo laſſen vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vviſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l14">daʒ die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> bede getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe cʒetel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l15">auſweiſt die Jr vns vormals darümb geſant habt / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l16">vvo vvir euch lıeb vnd dinſt <expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l17">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan></del> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ poſt Galli Anno M<hi rend="sup">o</hi>cccc <expan>duodecı<ex>m</ex>o</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_528" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Johan Adolff von Nassawe,
                                                sigeler czu Hoeste und probist czu Jecheburgk</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als
                                                wir euch vormals <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Wilhelm Rumels des
                                                  <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und Hansen
                                                Prünsters, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r,</ex></expan> wegen, darauff ir
                                                uns <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> wider
                                                  <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, ob
                                                  <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> das getan
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> als
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die czetele
                                                  <add>ynnehellet,</add> die ir <add>und wir
                                                  haben</add>, <add>oder ob</add> sie des noch niht
                                                getan <add><expan>hete<ex>n,</ex></expan></add> daz
                                                sie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das noch
                                                  <add>tun</add>, so wolt ir ein genüg daran
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; also lassen wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz die
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> bede getan
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die czetel ausweist,
                                                die ir uns vormals darümb gesant habt.
                                                  <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir euch lieb und
                                                dinst <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n,</ex></expan> das
                                                  <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> iiii post Galli anno
                                                  m<hi rend="sup">o</hi>cccc
                                                  <expan>duodeci<ex>m</ex>o.</expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
